{
  "chapter": 92,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十二回「假掌门」。芮玮在鹦鹉洲面对简召舞冒充月形门掌门的局面。简召舞以玄龟集为掌门信符，逼迫芮玮承认其掌门身份。芮玮当众行大礼却只喊\"哥哥\"而非\"掌门\"，巧妙回避了认其为掌门。丑老尼秋萍揭示秦百龄是白燕的生父，秋萍为救秦百龄断其一臂后自断一臂，但仍被月形门大圆阵困住。简召舞命三长老擒拿白燕等无影门四女，银月以四象阵抵挡。关键时刻，芮玮出示万有全遗物，令三位长老退出是非之地。芮玮又揭露齐治平胸前并无半月青记，证明其假月形门弟子身份，继而指出简召舞亦非真弟子。简召舞见大势已去，弃去掌门之位，转而以铁网帮主身份煽动帮众围攻芮玮等人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "固长老、单长老、简长老，本门律法不听命掌门者如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "三长老",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不听掌门命者，同门共愤，理处极刑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此说可无假吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "兄弟！你自承认月形门弟子，这声兄弟，你意如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "长老是月形门硕果仅存的老前辈，晚辈后进，愧不敢当兄弟之称！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "本门虽重辈分，然而我一门皆是兄弟，在你我辈分未明之前，我先喊你一声兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我很高兴本门武学在你身上放一异彩，纵观本门有始以来，武学以你空前绝后。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "武学绝顶，对本门来说，固一喜事，然则，不能叫武学绝顶便就轻视了本门礼法，兄弟！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你若仍自承月形门弟子，请在众人面前凝重地宣称一次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xin",
      "speaker_name": "素心",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_su_xin",
      "text": "野儿，什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_xin",
      "speaker_name": "素心",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你，你要知道那恶人现是月形门的掌门……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_su_xin",
      "text": "野儿，你放心。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本人芮玮月形门弟子，凡我门中理法绝不敢有所违背！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好！好！本人也以长老身份承认你是月形门弟子。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄弟快来见过本门掌门。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "掌门在此！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "请恕晚辈不知，三位长老，何以证明他是掌门。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "单鹤、简虎",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，不得无礼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_he",
      "speaker_name": "单鹤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "对掌门的身份，岂可怀疑！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_dan_he",
      "text": "晚辈不知！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有我兄弟三人承认，浑装什么不知！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_jian_hu",
      "text": "简兄弟，不可如此武断，有我兄弟三人承认不足为重，因将事实证明他看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "掌门，请将掌门信符取出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这是本门秘术总鉴，在此堪称本门掌门信符！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_he",
      "speaker_name": "单鹤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，你现在还有怀疑吗！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快去见过掌门！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "起来！起来！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "哥哥！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你，你是什么意思……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此中情由，不细言。各位必定早巳怀疑为何我的容貌与他相似得难以辨认，实在他乃是我的哥哥，他本人不知，我却知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "恭喜掌门有这么位身手绝顶的弟弟。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕儿！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "法师，请将秦百龄交我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "娘，你就将秦老儿交给他们吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "你再不助我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "燕儿，你忍心见他被世敌擒去，受辱而死？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "燕儿，你实不该喊他秦老儿，可知他是……他是……他是你的父亲！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "无影门弟子何来父亲，你，你……骗我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "我不骗你，秦百龄之于我，正等于芮玮之于你般，你当知'衣馥'的父亲是谁！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "真……真的……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "你们就把我杀了吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "法师，你已出家为尼，何必再恋旧情！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_he",
      "speaker_name": "单鹤",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "你想让他废去一臂吗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "法师，请将秦百龄放下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟三人门下亲传弟子守在鹦鹉洲附近出路，任谁也难脱走，法师，我劝你还是将秦百龄放下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们将他拿去吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "法师放心，秦百龄虽然落到我们手中，却不一定对他有何剧烈的行动，咱们只要太阳门掌门被囚于月形门弟子手中！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_jian_hu",
      "text": "简兄弟，你将秦百龄抱进内堂，替他疗伤止血。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "丑老尼",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "我断了你父一臂，也……也当自断一臂……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_chou_lao_ni",
      "text": "你，你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "怎么免动于戈？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "请你们自动至刑堂发落，你们受雇于人，当可酌量减刑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么减刑法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "依情至少断去双臂。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢如此宽待啦！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "若不自动就审，就无如此优待。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "自动就审说难听点，可是自动就缚？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "就是如此！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们无芮公子相助，寡不敌众，只有自动就缚一途了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可是芮公子呀，你难道没有杀害本门弟子，不是也该自动就缚受刑吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "还不就缚！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_he",
      "speaker_name": "单鹤",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "你们自量能逃得脱吗，自动就缚，免除死刑。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "论理，咱们识时务的话，应该自动就缚，然则在未就缚以前，我无影门有点小要求。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "什么要求？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "我无影门有个规矩，凡相害咱们相干之人，必处死刑，那位老尼不用说了，就是秦老儿亦是咱们相干之人，他两人各断一臂，追究起来贵掌门与三位实是相害者，所以嘛据理死刑难免，但你们宽待咱们，咱们也大方一次，我说你们请贵掌门即刻各自断去一臂，谢罪罢！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "这就是你所提的要求吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "是呀！等你们断去一臂后，咱们却就自动就缚。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": "char_yin_yue",
      "text": "臭丫头，找死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_yue",
      "speaker_name": "银月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四象阵！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "三位长老暂停攻击。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对方以四人布成阵法，咱们同时以四人破他阵法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮兄弟，请你下场一助三长老。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "兄弟请占丙丁位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "固长老，我不是来助你们破阵的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "简虎",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不听掌门之命吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不可不听掌门之命。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "我不认他为本门掌门。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dan_he",
      "speaker_name": "单鹤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "君子岂可出尔反尔！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_dan_he",
      "text": "我只认他哥哥，并未认他掌门，掌门之命不可不听，然他并非本门掌门，命令自可不听了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你为何不认他掌门，可有什么道理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gu_peng",
      "text": "固长老请过来看看这是什么东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倘若以万老前辈的遗物作掌门信物的话，在下也要以掌门自居了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_peng",
      "speaker_name": "固鹏",
      "listener": "char_dan_he",
      "text": "单兄弟，简兄弟，咱们不便再插手其间，退出这是非场所可好？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "三长老",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "恕难从命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "齐治平",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，速听掌门之命，擒拿四位蒙面女子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "你是月形门下的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "齐治平",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这还有假！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "月形门弟子胸前以半月为记，你可有吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "齐治平",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "当然有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "让我看看。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要害羞，让大家看看。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "接我一掌！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "请问阁下青记何在，莫非是隐形的吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "齐治平",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我无半月形青记，你自承月形门弟子可也有吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不妨看看。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "齐老师，倘若贵掌门是真正的月形门弟子，可请他一示胸膛。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "齐治平",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不，不用看了……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "那么在下岂能草率奉行身份未明的掌门之命？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_qi_zhi_ping",
      "text": "齐老师回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，你不听我这掌门之命，其实我并不希罕这掌门，从今后弃去也罢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "本该如此，你冒充月形门弟子，更不惜命齐治平假装投效，引诱真正的月形门弟子出来，其心意不过为增加自己的实力，其实这又何必，你阴谋夺取铁网帮主之位已经够了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我铁网帮众满布此地，你们要想生离此地，除非先将我帮兄弟全部杀了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "御敌不侮，辱则必强！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在咱们遭到强敌，死伤帮众，这口气能不能忍受？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能忍受……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "辱则必强，咱们不能忘了老帮主的训示，要替死去的帮众复仇，断断不能放过杀伤本帮弟子的凶手！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    }
  ],
